tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:19:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽人講食咗可以痾屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f797bbba77751b72c49684c29dca166c82b465","tid":143062,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>需要原因咩</blockquote><br />\n總會有嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8870c2935de0484624a308e00ca82e96c85d5f81","tid":143062,"uid":78082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:22:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>讀大學Year1見識到唔同既人<br />\n有好多出類拔萃既人，好多有錢人<br />\n自己屋企，甚至中學既圈子其實都係社會既低下層<br />\n就算讀到U，都已經輸左係起跑線<br />\n同想象落差太大，好迷網</blockquote><br />\n咁就要食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食煙唔需要咩好慘既理由</blockquote><br />\n可以咁講<br />\n果年18歲，人生無受過咩大既挫折同打擊<br />\n有D經歷令個價值觀突然轉變左<br />\n當時覺得身邊既人唔會明<br />\n最後走去試下食煙黎抒發<br />\n<br />\n而家食左8年又見識多左<br />\n諗返轉頭緊係覺得好小事"},{"pid":"937d5854a2c48c28787e560ad5ce3a243cc6fa1b","tid":143062,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:22:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老豆迫我試</blockquote><br />\n點解要咁做？</blockquote><br />\n我讀小學個陣我老豆腦筍都未生埋,又迫我飲酒又迫我食煙,之後佢因為打劫坐撚左監,我老母即刻搬屋換電話,以後都冇左見過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da5836a269337df9139666df2d9445d03ed3e2d","tid":143062,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:22:11.000Z","msg":"我想放棄自己"},{"pid":"d9ef537894873b3a2ccdd6037f9a168e7a72a5d2","tid":143062,"uid":57255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:25:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>信咗啲人話可以減壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果10分鐘內的確係既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3546798ee50f33135c5a6a7c6125e614f2422a5","tid":143062,"uid":78082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:27:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n我好慘都無食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係慘先有資格食煙既<br />\n分享下點解會食第一支煙姐<br />\nbtw 屋企有人食煙都有d影響"},{"pid":"cef43b3e6437cc46218931e4f40cc373e72f0abc","tid":143062,"uid":3527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:29:33.000Z","msg":"因為聽講食一手煙同二手煙唔同，老豆一路食開，細個叫佢戒唔戒，咁就想試下係咩感覺，點解咁難戒<br />\n<br />\n食完之後即刻有屎痾，得閒無聊無嘢做又可以放下煙brake ，落地盤班師父又會一齊一路食一路吹水一路做，有嘢諗唔明就自己一個係樓下公園食住煙飲住酒諗，好free <br />\n<br />\n但我唔鼓勵人食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80414127afdf3a74903e3bc9345d1942878575d","tid":143062,"uid":3527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想放棄自己</blockquote><br />\n呢個都係其中一個食煙原因，慢性自殺，等老豆老母過咗生之後自己都唔會放得耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2afc88ca07f5347fd30e25af7060c30574dd72d0","tid":143062,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:33:01.000Z","msg":"因為同ex吵"},{"pid":"a1d72565b360fda1e291a92c023aeccb0b4df046","tid":143062,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為聽講食一手煙同二手煙唔同，老豆一路食開，細個叫佢戒唔戒，咁就想試下係咩感覺，點解咁難戒<br />\n<br />\n食完之後即刻有屎痾，得閒無聊無嘢做又可以放下煙brake ，落地盤班師父又會一齊一路食一路吹水一路做，有嘢諗唔明就自己一個係樓下公園食住煙飲住酒諗，好free <br />\n<br />\n但我唔鼓勵人食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食煙真係通便？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果依家要你戒<br />\n你戒唔戒到？"},{"pid":"ffd817caea8b5bbe254f93b1081be5b25ba32d73","tid":143062,"uid":13263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:36:33.000Z","