ockquote><br />\n只可以講一手煙同二手煙係唔同味唔同感覺，我會食但都唔鐘意一陣煙味/二手煙<br />\n戒唔戒到睇自己定力"},{"pid":"e4179e00bc3f9d58db2542ccd042c691443e8c9a","tid":143062,"uid":1878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:44:25.000Z","msg":"有人淨係打煙炮，唔扯肺？感覺上健康好多"},{"pid":"95b2d3f1a5ea6df41e065b58da0335be87e5730a","tid":143062,"uid":77844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:44:48.000Z","msg":"見個fd又要食又要戒想試下點解會咁<br />\n結果好難食 人生食過一枝咁大把"},{"pid":"5b12614c855e63249d2883e3bbcdfd213aabd833","tid":143062,"uid":39785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:45:20.000Z","msg":"好臭呀你"},{"pid":"68d9626900a631ca2e2f17d6b5598202be436d55","tid":143062,"uid":6936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:56:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有時吸到二手煙會肚痛 想柯屎</blockquote><br />\n二手煙就唔知，但食一手薄荷煙真係會通便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />肚痛就係另一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每次食都好急屎急尿</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40136003ef6524687c9c9552beb8f02eeb80b11","tid":143062,"uid":33040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:56:46.000Z","msg":"未試過試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7637d93c9c67b687e4af9a2b93beb32f3e4a7e","tid":143062,"uid":6936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人淨係打煙炮，唔扯肺？感覺上健康好多</blockquote><br />\n師兄，打煙炮不如唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食煙就一定唔健康架啦。想有feel咪扯肺囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79955b94beb9838fe2db863aa395dd96da0c79c","tid":143062,"uid":15800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:59:31.000Z","msg":"因為青梅竹馬比人搶走<br />\n同個fd呻緊既時候就食左<br />\n<br />\n之後一唔開心就食<br />\n之後就係同fd傾計就一齊食，打牌都一路食<br />\n<br />\n不過前排頭暈左成個月，行路都飄飄下<br />\n戒曬所有壞習慣，順便戒埋煙"},{"pid":"8f566349d09e3a63155243530565a655769572b9","tid":143062,"uid":15800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人淨係打煙炮，唔扯肺？感覺上健康好多</blockquote><br />\n比人見到打煙炮都幾柒下<br />\n唔食煙既人未必知<br />\n有食一定睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7697e85ed7c780fa277eae4296ab4f1a97df88dc","tid":143062,"uid":29946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:13:05.000Z","msg":"有時候生活太大壓力 要放鬆下🚬"},{"pid":"bf649b1cbc7af9e689b9dd4e2655dce3ea3e8627","tid":143062,"uid":63684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:27:25.000Z","msg":"酒 煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42026044c0dbf03e2f9d3f4470b819e5d6ace1e3","tid":143062,"uid":77481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同人開片，個friend用腳夾俾我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來你仲未死"},{"pid":"049706f0f00ca92f3cf176754a80d1c0ab0eeb28","tid":143062,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:38:27.000Z","msg":"同咗個食煙嘅女仔一齊<br />\n一開始幫佢點煙 買煙<br />\n後期自己食埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb8b2e938a62a0200d34d31567081e02b3b37a1b","tid":143062,"uid":88933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"訓導主任教我食"},{"pid":"57a455bf5b7bd6e8de98a87a349ece47a53671d7","tid":143062,"uid":15514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:49:53.000Z","msg":"有晚做做下hon pro諗唔到野 <br />\n第一枝係捲煙 一食就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後試過綠luck 藍莓5 黑冰"}]}